1
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:51,160
Zhiyong, move that table over here.

2
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:51,920
Align it to the right.

3
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,450
This one.

4
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:53,920
Yes.

5
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,600
The pen fell.

6
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,800
Yuanbao, let me help you.

7
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,080
No need.

8
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,080
I can do it myself.

9
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,720
Yuanbao,

10
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,560
didn't we agree to be sisters?

11
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,080
You don't need to be so polite to me.

12
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,280
Besides, as a girl,

13
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,640
how can you carry such heavy water?

14
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,500
Let me help you.

15
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:17,400
No need.

16
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,760
Really no need. I can do it.

17
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,560
You still have a waist injury.

18
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,920
You should be careful yourself.

19
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,960
It's fine. My waist is much better now.

20
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,960
Helping you carry water is no problem.

21
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,560
It's okay.

22
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,500
Really no need.

23
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,400
Really.

24
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,760
Xinrui.

25
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,720
It's fine.

26
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,040
Sorry, Xinrui.

27
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:41,240
I didn't mean to.

28
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,640
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

29
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,400
She has a back injury.

30
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,360
I know. I...

31
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,880
Jingu, don't blame Yuanbao.

32
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,920
It's all my fault.

33
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,760
I insisted on helping her.

34
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:52,100
She didn't push me on purpose.

35
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,280
Yuanbao, I'm sorry.

36
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,240
I just lost my balance.

37
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,850
Please don't be mad.

38
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:01,560
What's wrong?

39
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,240
It's nothing.

40
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,280
Don't make such a fuss.

41
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,360
Yuanbao,

42
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,800
I'm taking Xinrui to the infirmary.

43
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,200
Okay, go ahead.

44
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:19,040
I just gave her a push.

45
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,920
Why did she fall?

46
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,160
Ruirui.

47
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,380
I'm here for class too.

48
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,090
Why are you here too?

49
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,960
I didn't do well on the last exam,

50
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,450
so my mom dumped me here.

51
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,800
She said she never wants to sit in

52
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,760
that special seat for parents again.

53
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,480
She said someone here can watch me do my homework,

54
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,340
which is great.

55
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,160
Ruirui,

56
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,120
don't you think

57
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,360
it's fate that brought us together?

58
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,240
Stop being so cheesy.

59
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,800
Does your mom hit you a lot?

60
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,680
Not a lot.

61
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,920
Only when I get bad grades

62
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,200
or make her mad,

63
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,730
she occasionally disciplines me.

64
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:27,680
Even though you bicker with your mom,

65
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,200
I always feel

66
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:32,280
you two actually have a pretty good relationship.

67
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,080
Yeah.

68
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,040
My dad passed away early.

69
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,240
My mom had to provide for the family

70
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,920
and take care of me and my sister.

71
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,520
It's really not easy for her.

72
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,820
Also, these past couple of years,

73
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:50,170
she hasn't been in good health.

74
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,380
The doctor told her to exercise more.

75
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,720
But my mom is so lazy.

76
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,560
She doesn't want to move.

77
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,480
So I have to use this method

78
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,540
to force her to move

79
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,880
and run more.

80
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,640
You piss her off on purpose

81
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,400
to make her chase you?

82
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,600
That's how you help her.

83
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,560
Smart, right?

84
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,040
Aren't you afraid

85
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,920
of giving her high blood pressure?

86
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,920
No.

87
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,000
My mom is the kind of person

88
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,440
whose bark is worse than her bite when she's angry.

89
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,160
She doesn't take things to heart.

90
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,680
Even if she really gets angry,

91
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,880
she'll be fine after beating me up.

92
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,680
It's also a good workout for her.

93
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,810
It's quite good.

94
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,930
What kind of twisted logic is that?

95
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,840
I'm not cut out for studying.

96
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:42,210
And I don't have any special strengths

97
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,960
for my mom to brag about.

98
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,940
So I have to use this method

99
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,600
to help her out.

100
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,120
What's wrong?

101
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,200
Did I scare you?

102
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,000
No.

103
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,880
Why aren't you saying anything?

104
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:01,360
Actually, I understand you perfectly.

105
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,880
My mom is quite busy.

106
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,240
She has no time for me.

107
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:09,100
My mom and I have been in a cold war for a while.

108
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:11,720
I'm planning to go live at my grandma's.

109
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,520
You can't do that.

110
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,120
You two are mother and daughter.

111
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,520
It should be easy to communicate.

112
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,440
Just talk more.

113
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,780
It's not easy being children,

114
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,360
but it's even harder being parents.

115
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,690
I didn't expect you to be so mature about this.

116
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,320
Well.

117
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:35,000
Tell you what. If you have any problems you don't know how to solve,

118
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,760
just ask me. I'll teach you.

119
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,560
Really?

120
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,480
Okay, you said it.

121
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,370
Don't find me annoying.

122
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,040
Not annoying at all.

123
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,000
Alright, everyone, quiet down.

124
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,530
We are about to start class.

125
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:13,320
Since we were young,

126
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:16,080
your notes have always been neat and clean.

127
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:20,200
Reading your notes is such a pleasure.

128
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,520
The key points in this notebook

129
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,050
are written in such detail.

130
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,680
You always get a perfect score in physics.

131
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,740
Do you still need to make these notes?

132
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,120
You can do it, Yuanbao.

133
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,960
I thought you made this especially for me.

134
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,930
I'll make one for you later.

135
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:50,159
Are you and Yuanbao close?

136
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:53,650
We're desk-mates, so naturally we're close.

137
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,290
We just help each other out.

138
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,560
Closer than we are?

139
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,330
It's different.

140
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:04,090
Have you finished writing your notes?

141
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,360
Done.

142
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,480
Actually, I like Yuanbao too.

143
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,280
I want to be friends with her.

144
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,800
But I'm afraid

145
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,720
that because of the water-carrying incident today,

146
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,320
she won't come near me again.

147
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,800
Why don't you help me, Jingu?

148
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,200
What do you mean?

149
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:25,880
Guess.

150
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,640
Pass the ball.

151
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,360
No one is defending him.

152
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,200
Shoot.

153
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:34,480
Missed.

154
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,059
Class is over. Gather around.

155
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,000
Mu Qingyun.

156
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,320
What's wrong?

157
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,880
The final exam is coming.

158
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,920
During this time, I plan to spend half an hour every day after school

159
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,320
tutoring Yuanbao.

160
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:57,240
I will walk her home after tutoring.

161
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,360
So,

162
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,160
you don't need to wait for her after school.

163
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,440
Stop it.

164
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,400
Ruirui.

165
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:11,800
Blockhead.

166
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,890
What's going on?

167
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:46,250
Later, based on your ability and foundation,

168
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,000
I'll put together a set of

169
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,610
physics summaries for you.

170
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,480
Class,

171
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:28,320
I have an announcement before we start.

172
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,520
Gu Xinrui has a notebook

173
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,720
that went missing in the classroom.

174
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,640
Gu Xinrui,

175
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:33,480
what kind of notebook was it?

176
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,960
It was about this big,

177
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:38,400
filled with physics notes.

178
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,490
I put it on my desk this morning,

179
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,920
but it was gone after PE class.

180
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,080
Come on, class.

181
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:47,000
Check your backpacks, drawers,

182
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,240
and desks.

183
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,540
Let's help her find it.

184
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,520
That's the one.

185
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,720
No.

186
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,560
I don't know why

187
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,220
this notebook is here with me.

188
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,000
No, I mean,

189
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,410
I really didn't take it.

190
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,560
Yuanbao, it's okay.

191
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:21,880
This notebook

192
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,520
was organized by Meng Jingu

193
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,520
to give to you.

194
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:26,220
He just lent it to me first.

195
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:29,200
Now that it's in your hands,

196
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,600
let's just forget it.

197
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,440
Sir, it's fine.

198
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,520
Okay.

199
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:34,800
No.

200
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,240
I really don't know

201
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,700
why this notebook is here.

202
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,680
I really didn't take it.

203
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:41,320
No one said you stole it.

204
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,730
Don't be so anxious.

205
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,620
It couldn't be Xiong Yuanbao.

206
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,680
Why would she take your notebook?

207
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,720
Exactly.

208
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:50,880
If Yuanbao stole bread or sausages,

209
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,080
I could understand.

210
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,280
Stealing a notebook?

211
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,560
Impossible.

212
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,720
Definitely.

213
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,600
What are you laughing at?

214
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,890
Yuanbao doesn't know what's going on.

215
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:05,080
I put the notebook in Yuanbao's drawer.

216
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,240
Weren't you nagging this morning

217
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,920
that you needed to give this notebook to Yuanbao?

218
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:09,760
Yuanbao wasn't here,

219
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,490
so you asked me to give it to her.

220
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:15,120
I forgot.

221
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,520
Sorry, Yuanbao.

222
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,840
I told you.

223
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,040
I can understand Yuanbao stealing food.

224
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,000
Stealing a notebook?

225
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,920
You're kidding.

226
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:23,080
Of course.

227
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:23,880
All right.

228
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,320
Since it's a misunderstanding, it's fine.

229
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,480
Go back to your seats.

230
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,200
Take out your test papers.

231
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,730
We'll continue to go over yesterday's paper.

232
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,240
Villain.

233
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:42,120
So the answer to question 4 is A.

234
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,480
Do you all get it?

235
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,360
Question 4.

236
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,240
Got it.

237
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,560
Now let's do the next question.

238
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,760
Final exams are coming up soon.

239
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,880
Every day after school during this period,

240
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,940
how about I tutor you for half an hour?

241
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,520
No need to trouble yourself.

242
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:07,000
I can study by myself when I go home at night.

243
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,840
Thanks, deskmate.

244
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:23,220
You finally remembered to treat me to ice cream.

245
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,220
I've kept them all in mind.

246
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:27,080
I was just saving them up for you.

247
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:29,050
At least you have a conscience.

248
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:31,760
Blockhead.

249
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,090
Thank you for today.

250
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,720
Why are you thanking me all of a sudden?

251
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:38,040
I mean about the notebook today.

252
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:40,600
I know you didn't put it in my drawer.

253
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:42,680
How do you know?

254
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,760
If it were really you,

255
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,880
with Gu Xinrui looking for it for so long,

256
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,610
you would have said it long ago.

257
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:50,920
Waiting until everyone suspected me

258
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:51,920
to stand up for me,

259
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:54,850
I know you were trying to get me out of trouble.

260
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,400
You've grown a brain.

261
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,340
Didn't you suspect I stole it?

262
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:06,440
With your brain, stealing?

263
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,720
If you could steal things,

264
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,640
then I could buy a house on Mars.

265
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,400
You believe in me that much?

266
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,170
Even if the whole world doubts you,

267
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,600
I wouldn't suspect you.

268
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:27,530
How was that?

269
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,680
It's a new line I learned.

270
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:30,410
Did it sound cool when I said it?

271
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,640
By the way, when is your dad coming back?

272
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,600
My dad?

273
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,800
I called him.

274
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:41,100
He said he inspected the area for a while,

275
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,840
and it's not bad,

276
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,170
so he's staying to work.

277
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,650
What about you and your mom?

278
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:48,280
Of course my mom and I are staying.

279
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,240
Why are you looking like that?

280
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,570
Trying to drive us away?

281
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,880
Not exactly.

282
00:14:58,920 --> 00:14:59,650
Don't worry.

283
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,490
Even if we really have to go,

284
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,080
we won't abandon you and Grandma.

285
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:07,120
If we leave, we leave together.

286
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,960
We are a family.

287
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,600
Ever since the notebook incident,

288
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,400
I don't know why,

289
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,480
I've been deliberately

290
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,560
keeping my distance from Meng Jingu.

291
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:32,160
With the first year of high school ending

292
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:33,920
and class division coming up in the second year,

293
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:36,650
I wanted to devote myself entirely to my studies.

294
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,440
However, more often than not,

295
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:41,120
things don't go as we expect.

296
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,400
Surprises and accidents

297
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,930
always come unexpectedly.

298
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,080
Freshman year is almost over.

299
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,340
I got you a little gift.

300
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:50,960
For me?

301
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:52,440
Of course.

302
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:54,720
Take it.

303
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,130
I picked it out just for you.

304
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,480
I hope you like it.

305
00:15:58,880 --> 00:15:59,640
What is it?

306
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:00,760
Open it and see.

307
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,280
A puzzle.

308
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,720
All right.

309
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,400
I'll do it with Ruirui,

310
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,720
so it'll be faster.

311
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:12,400
No.

312
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:16,720
My secret is written

313
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,920
on the back.

314
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,640
Besides you,

315
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,160
no one else can know.

316
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:25,480
Okay then, I'll do it secretly by myself

317
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,850
and not tell anyone.

318
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,280
Yuanbao.

319
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,600
Are you still mad at me

320
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,200
about the notebook incident

321
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,120
last time?

322
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,880
Why would I be mad at you?

323
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,760
Xinrui grabbed it from me,

324
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,360
saying she wanted to give it to you herself.

325
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:48,120
Mutou already explained this to me.

326
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:49,690
It's in the past.

327
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,090
You have grass on your head.

328
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,119
Let's go.

329
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,840
Did you make up with your desk mate again?

330
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,520
What do you mean made up?

331
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:00,520
Don't talk nonsense.

332
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:02,320
We've always been on good terms.

333
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,480
What's in such a big box?

334
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:08,240
A puzzle.

335
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:10,970
How unoriginal.

336
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,880
As if yours are creative.

337
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:17,040
You either give caterpillars or dead mice.

338
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:52,160
This should be the last time

339
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:54,020
writing Class 20, Grade 1, right?

340
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:41,760
Hello, Mr. Liu.

341
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:42,620
Hello, Mr. Liu.

342
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:47,080
Mr. Liu Li.

343
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:50,240
Ms. Xu.

344
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:51,440
Well,

345
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:53,560
isn't this semester ending soon?

346
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,980
Time flies, and it's hard to say goodbye.

347
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:57,840
Thank you for taking care of me.

348
00:19:57,840 --> 00:20:00,770
So I brought some local specialties from my hometown

349
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:01,680
for you.

350
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:04,280
I'm so thrilled.

351
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,040
Listen,

352
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:08,300
call me anytime if you need anything.

353
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:10,360
I'll be there for you right away.

354
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,720
Please continue to look after me next semester.

355
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,520
Okay.

356
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:15,080
See you next semester then.

357
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,320
Okay, no problem.

358
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:17,040
Bye.

359
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:19,280
You can call me during the holidays.

360
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,600
My phone is on 24/7.

361
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,280
Okay.

362
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:26,000
Tian Yong.

363
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:30,360
The eggs Ms. Xu gave me.

364
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,570
Are you jealous?

365
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,560
We all have them.

366
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:38,280
Two boxes.

367
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:45,640
I have some too.

368
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,410
Did you know?

369
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:58,760
Tong Ruirui and her mom went on a trip.

370
00:21:00,120 --> 00:21:01,080
Xing Yaqi is going to Beijing next month

371
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:02,440
for a summer camp.

372
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:05,560
Gao Jingyi is visiting her relatives.

373
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,800
During this wonderful time,

374
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:11,120
we're stuck at home doing homework.

375
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,600
Life is so unfair.

376
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,880
What? You want to go out and play?

377
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,200
Don't you?

378
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:22,300
Last time we went to Shanghai,

379
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:24,330
we didn't have time to look around.

380
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:26,450
I wonder when we'll go there again.

381
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:30,800
What if we apply to a university

382
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:32,880
in Shanghai in the future?

383
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:37,180
I still want to go to a university in Beijing.

384
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:40,520
Don't limit yourself.

385
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,960
A real man should have high ambitions

386
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,360
and let his talents soar.

387
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,000
Fly where?

388
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,410
With your grades, where can you fly to?

389
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,880
Summer vacation is the best time to review.

390
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,060
Ask Yuanbao if you don't know.

391
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,960
Your midterm exams were fine,

392
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:00,640
but how many places did you drop in the final exam?

393
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,680
Don't even think about going anywhere this summer.

394
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,610
Stay home and review your lessons.

395
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,840
Mom. Auntie.

396
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,160
Don't call me mom.

397
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,000
Study.

398
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:16,120
My mom's been nagging about my grades

399
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:17,560
for half the vacation.

400
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,640
I'm telling you, my mom's nagging skills

401
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,970
aren't something just anyone can master.

402
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,600
Look at Meng Jingu's notes.

403
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,410
Don't let them mislead you.

404
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:34,000
What do you know?

405
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,080
With this,

406
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:37,440
it's like having a secret martial arts manual.

407
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,880
It gets twice the result with half the effort.

408
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,680
It's the essence of the essence.

409
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:44,440
I think my mom is really right.

410
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,480
Your grades shouldn't have dropped.

411
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:49,480
Why did they drop?

412
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:51,560
Don't you know?

413
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:55,130
That's because the questions this time were too hard, okay?

414
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:58,650
I'm not talking to you anymore.

415
00:22:58,840 --> 00:22:59,840
My stomach hurts.

416
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:07,480
Grandma, my stomach hurts.

417
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,280
Go quickly, go.

418
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:11,410
I'll find you some medicine later.

419
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:26,840
This kid really has a way.

420
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:30,880
What new trick is in this gift box?

421
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:38,250
What is this?

422
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,720
A puzzle.

423
00:23:44,320 --> 00:23:45,280
With words on it.

424
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:48,820
This kid really has a lot of tricks up his sleeve.

425
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:52,010
Yuanbao's grades dropped so much because of him.

426
00:23:52,040 --> 00:23:54,570
And now he's distracting her with this stuff.

427
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:01,360
This guy.

428
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,880
Meng Jingu, you really have some tricks.

429
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:06,730
Who could possibly solve this?

430
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:14,400
Clever kid.

431
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,880
I knew there was a message.

432
00:24:27,080 --> 00:24:28,400
Are you...

433
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,560
using secret codes, kid?

434
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,360
What is this?

435
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:35,120
Would you my Zi be...

436
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:37,120
Would you

437
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:39,880
be my...

438
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,800
Would you be my Zixia?

439
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:50,810
You little rascal, Meng Jingu.

440
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,440
Impossible.

441
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:55,560
Keep

442
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,260
dreaming. In your dreams!

443
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,960
Why are there so many?

444
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,480
How can I tell them apart?

445
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:07,920
Yuanbao.

446
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:09,680
Grandma.

447
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:15,240
You got a lot today.

448
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:22,200
You eat so little every night.

449
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:23,840
I don't dare to cook too much.

450
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:24,700
Are you hungry?

451
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:26,280
I'll go get you something to eat.

452
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:27,400
It's okay, Grandma.

453
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,960
I'm not hungry. Make less.

454
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:30,800
I heard

455
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,200
eating too much will make me stupid.

456
00:25:33,280 --> 00:25:34,840
Okay, I'll listen to you.

457
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:40,880
Isn't it a bit immoral not to let her see it?

458
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,400
Grandma, where is Yuanbao?

459
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:02,180
He has a stomachache. He's in the toilet.

460
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:05,080
I left something behind. I'll go get it.

461
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:06,160
Okay, go ahead.

462
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:54,120
It's so much, it will take me forever to finish.

463
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:58,200
I still want to take some extra classes this summer vacation.

464
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,060
Morning, Grandma.

465
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:03,960
It's summer vacation, I want you to sleep more,

466
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,220
so I didn't wake you up.

467
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,080
Breakfast is on the table.

468
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:08,000
Go eat.

469
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:13,200
Mutou, why are you so early?

470
00:27:16,040 --> 00:27:17,920
What's wrong? Do you have a cold?

471
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,080
Yeah.

472
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:19,960
Didn't you say that this summer,

473
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,440
you wanted to catch up on your studies?

474
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:22,480
So I asked Xing Yaqi

475
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:24,120
for her notebook and made a copy.

476
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:26,520
It's definitely better than Meng Jingu's.

477
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:27,280
Take a look.

478
00:27:29,560 --> 00:27:30,160
My god.

479
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,840
This is exactly what I've been dreaming of.

480
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:37,080
Our class monitor never disappoints.

481
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,760
It's so detailed.

482
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:42,680
It's just that someone's handwriting is a bit ugly.

483
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,640
Mutou, you are so good to me.

484
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,080
Tell me,

485
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:50,960
how do you want me to reward you?

486
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:52,920
Up to you.

487
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,500
I'm going back.

488
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:00,920
Mutou.

489
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,640
Why does he have a fever?

490
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:16,360
I don't know what he was tinkering with last night.

491
00:28:16,360 --> 00:28:17,560
He was at it all night.

492
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,680
I saw him writing something when I got up to use the bathroom.

493
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,740
I just ignored him.

494
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,560
And he had a fever this morning.

495
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,040
I've told him so many times

496
00:28:24,120 --> 00:28:25,000
not to stay up late,

497
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,280
but he just wouldn't listen.

498
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:27,080
Now he's sick.

499
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,160
It's okay.

500
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:30,370
I just wiped him down with alcohol.

501
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:32,240
He also took some fever medicine.

502
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:34,840
He just needs to sweat it out under the blanket.

503
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:38,810
Is the ginger soup still boiling on the stove?

504
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:41,280
Look at my memory.

505
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:43,700
I forgot to turn off the stove.

506
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,920
I'll go change his water.

507
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,120
Call me if you need anything.

508
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:49,680
Okay.

509
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,120
Now you're sick.

510
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:05,720
You're usually so bossy,

511
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:07,130
and always bullying me.

512
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:15,330
Why is he burning up so much?

513
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:16,480
No.

514
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:18,680
I have to go buy a fever patch.

515
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:51,380
What are you doing?

516
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,960
You almost crushed me to death.

517
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,320
When have I ever bullied you?

518
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,640
Weren't you asleep?

519
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:06,200
You guys woke me up.

520
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:09,090
How are you feeling now?

521
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,260
Has your fever gone down a bit?

522
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:15,400
Don't move.

523
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:17,640
You need to rest more when you're sick.

524
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,760
Well, I...

525
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,120
What do you mean 'I'?

526
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:23,260
You're usually as strong as an ox.

527
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:25,290
How come you're so fragile now?

528
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,440
I think

529
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:28,440
I should just call you Lin Meimei from now on.

530
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,960
Catching a breeze and staying up late,

531
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,520
and you get a fever like this.

532
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,120
If your fever continues like this,

533
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:34,580
you're going to be cooked.

534
00:30:35,080 --> 00:30:36,000
I... no.

535
00:30:36,120 --> 00:30:36,680
No.

536
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:39,120
Stop being stubborn.

537
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:40,200
Listen to me.

538
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:42,650
You need to keep warm when you're sick.

539
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:45,360
Sweat it out and stay under the covers.

540
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:48,210
Just lie down and tell me if you need anything.

541
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:50,760
Really? Then I'll say it.

542
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:54,120
If I don't go now,

543
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,970
I'm going to wet the bed.

544
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:01,440
Then go. Go.

545
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:08,600
I,

546
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:09,720
well...

547
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:11,160
Yuanbao.

548
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:14,640
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

549
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,240
Well, you...

550
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:18,960
What's wrong with me?

551
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,440
She should see the message

552
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:22,680
behind the puzzle in a while.

553
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,320
To copy notes for me,

554
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,960
he didn't sleep all night

555
00:31:33,120 --> 00:31:34,720
and made himself sick.

556
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,720
What a silly blockhead.
